data.description: ** PRICE REDUCTION** DO NOT MISS OUT!! This Gorgeous 3-bedroom property located the sought after  Serenity Shores is the one you've been looking for! Featuring fabulous open layout with a stunning kitchen featuring a beautiful granite kitchen island, dark espresso kitchen cabinets, RO System already installed. This layout is  perfect for entertaining along with the multi-sliders leading to the back patio. This home also features automatic rolling blinds throughout the home. This split floor plan offers a stunning master bedroom with double vanity and two closets. Off the garage is the perfect wine nook/ key drop. The garage is equipped with plenty of storage and an epoxy coated floor.
